    <briefdescription>
<para>Builder utility for constructing immutable free-body scene models. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Collects rigid bodies, their initial transforms, and collision shapes, then emits a <computeroutput><ref refid="structnovaphy_1_1_model" kindref="compound">Model</ref></computeroutput> snapshot suitable for simulation. </para>
